        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "test(qa): add script producer e2e fixtures",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFinishes the reusable script-producer part of step 1 of the real-E2E QA cleanup plan after #97915, and cleans up the broad transport-scenario re-export.\n\nThe goal is to make future script-to-QA migrations produce honest QA evidence without each scenario reimplementing artifact paths, evidence summaries, command logs, or child process timeout cleanup.\n\n## Why This Change Was Made\n\n- Adds `extensions/qa-lab/src/script-producer.ts` for shared QA script producer option parsing, artifact writes, evidence bundle generation, and bounded child-command execution inside the QA Lab-owned boundary.\n- Adds regression coverage for producer evidence output, command logging, timeout force-settlement, detached process-group cleanup, Windows `taskkill /T` command construction, and shared temp-dir cleanup.\n- Expands `scripts/qa/docker-e2e-lane.ts` with remaining existing Docker lane names and a `--list`/`--help` surface for QA scenario adapters.\n- Removes the broad re-export of `qa-transport-scenarios` from `live-transport-scenarios.ts`; callers should import the QA transport helpers directly from their canonical module.\n\n## User Impact\n\nNo taxonomy IDs or product runtime behavior change. This is QA infrastructure for making future QA Lab script producers more meaningful and less duplicated while preserving child-process cleanup for E2E/script producers.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/qa-lab/src/script-producer.test.ts --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs test/extension-test-boundary.test.ts --reporter=verbose`\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.extension-qa.config.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/qa-transport-scenarios.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/scenario-runtime-api.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/qa-channel-transport.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/crabline-transport.test.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/suite-runtime-flow.test.ts --reporter=dot`\n- `pnpm check:test-types`\n- `pnpm exec oxfmt --check extensions/qa-lab/src/script-producer.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/script-producer.test.ts scripts/qa/docker-e2e-lane.ts extensions/qa-lab/src/live-transports/shared/live-transport-scenarios.ts`\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode commit --commit HEAD` clean after accepted fixes\n",
        "branch": "dallin/qa-real-e2e-step1-foundation",
